quran[5]{c,v,t}:
  24,54,"An Nulaa…óo maakan …ďee naafiqii…ďe: ∆äoftee Alla …óofto…óon Nulaa…óo on, ka kene e ka gunndoo, si on huccitii gaayi e ko yamir…óon kon e …óoftagol …ďe kam…ďe …ói…óo; haray anndu ko fawii mo kanko, ko ko o fawaa kon immorde e yottinngol ngol, no fawii on onon kadi ko fawa…óon kon immorde e …óoftagol ngol e gollirgol ko O addi kon, si on …óoftorii mo gollugol ko o yamiri on kon gollugol e accugol ko o ha…ói on kon, on feeway faande e goonga kan, fawaaki Nulaa…óo on si wanaa yottinngol …ďanngungol, fawaaki mo fawugol on e dow peewal ngal, e doolugol on e dow maggal."
  24,55,"Alla Fodii …ďen gom…óin…ďe Mo jeyaa…ďe e moo…óon …ďe golli golle mo∆ī∆īe …óen, nde O wallata …ďe e dow ay…ďe ma…ď…ďe …ďen, o wa…óa …ďe lontii…ďe ka leydi yeru no O wa…óiranoo non …ďen gom…óin…ďe adii…ďe …ďe lontii…ďe e mayri, O Fodi …ďe nde O wa…óata diina ma…ď…ďe ka O weltorani …ďe kan -…óum le ko Diina Lislaamu kan- wee…ďuka Tedduka, O fodi …ďe O wattitanay …ďe …ďaawo kulol ma…ď…ďe ngol hoolaare. Yo …ďe rewam Min tun, wata …ďe sirkanam hay e huunde. Kala yeddu…óo …ďaawo on neema hara …ďen …óon ko kam…ďe woni yaltu…ďe …ďen gaayi …óoftaare Alla."
  24,56,"Tottiree Julde nden no haaniri non, jonnon Jakka jawle moo…óon …óen, …óoftoron kadi Nulaa…óo on gollugol ko o yamiri on kon e accugol ko o ha…ói on kon e muu…óum, jortagol on he…ďay Yurmeende Alla nden."
  24,57,"Wata a sikku -an Nulaa…óo- …ďen yeddu…ďe Alla …ďe laawoto Lam si Mi faalaama jippingol Lepte …óen e ma…ď…ďe, jaa∆īorde ma…ď…ďe nden √Ďalnde Darngal ko Jahannama. On mo Jahannama woni wattinirde mu'un pellet, haray wattabde makko nden bonii."
  24,58,"Ko onon yo gom…óin…ďe Alla, …ďe golliri Sari'a mo O wa…óani …ďe on, yo …óa…ď…ďu duŇčayee e moo…óon maccu…ďe moo…óon …ďen e hor…ďe moo…óon …ďen e sukaa…ďe moo…óon rim…ďe …ďen, …ďen …ďe yottaaki duu…ďi kellefuyee e waqtuuji tati: Ko adii Julde Subaka nden, waqtu wattitugol conci waalor…ói …óin e conci gollir…ói …óin, e ka waqtu jolloro tuma …ďortoto …óon conci moo…óon fii …óoykal njolloor, e ka …ďaawo Julde gee∆īe; sabu ko on fewndo …ďortoto…óon conci moo…óon gollir…ói …óin …ďorno…óon conci …óaanor…ói …óin, …óii waqtuuji …óoo tati ko awraaji moo…óon, wata …ďe naatu ka moo…óon e majji si wonaa …ďaawo duŇčayee moo…óon. Bakkaatu fawaaki on fii naatugol ma…ď…ďe hara …ďe cakkitinaaki, bakkaatu fawaaki …ďe ko wonaa e nder …óii…óoo immorde e waqtuuji. kam…ďe ko …ďe heewu…ďe wangagol, yoga e moo…óon kadi no liigoo ka yoga, gasataa ha…óugol …ďe naatugol e kala waqtu si wanaa …ďe duŇčini. Ko wano Alla …ďannginirani on nii √Īaawooje duŇčinagol ngol O …ďannginiranta on Aayeeje tinndin…óe e ko O Sar'inani on kon immorde e √Īaawooje. Alla ko Anndu…óo nafaaji jeyaa…ďe Makko …ďen ko O √Ďee√Īu…óo e nder wa…óanngol …ďe ngol √Īaawooje."